Scenario: create and remove form definition
Given basic organizational unit setup
When form definition named SomeForm is created
Then events formDefinitionCreated,formDefinitionAdded,descriptionChanged occurred

When form definition is removed
Then events formDefinitionRemoved occurred

Scenario: create form and add fields
Given basic organizational unit setup

When value definition named SomeType is created
And field definition named SomeField of type SomeType is created
And form definition named SomeForm is created
And events are cleared
And field definition SomeField is added to form SomeForm
Then events fieldAdded occurred

When field definition SomeField is removed from form SomeForm
Then events fieldRemoved occurred

When field definition SomeField is removed from form SomeForm
Then no events occurred
